'''李德爾氏綜合徵'''({{lang|en|Liddle's syndrome}}、假性醛固酮增多症)<ref name="#1">Liddle Syndrome|url =http://www.uptodate.com/contents/genetic-disorders-of-the-collecting-tubule-sodium-channel-liddles-syndrome-and-pseudohypoaldosteronism-type-1?source=search_result&search=liddle+syndrome&selectedTitle=1~17 {{Wayback|url=http://www.uptodate.com/contents/genetic-disorders-of-the-collecting-tubule-sodium-channel-liddles-syndrome-and-pseudohypoaldosteronism-type-1?source=search_result&search=liddle+syndrome&selectedTitle=1~17 |date=20191223160212 }}</ref>是[[常染色体|常染色体]][[顯性_(遺傳學)|顯性遺傳]](Dominance (genetics))疾病、特徵在於早期頻繁嚴重的[[高血壓|高血壓]]，以及與低血漿[[腎素|腎素]]活性、[[代謝性鹼中毒|代謝性鹼中毒]](metabolic alkalosis)、[[低鉀血症|低鉀血症]]、及垂直相關於低醛固酮水平。<ref name="#1"/>

李德爾氏綜合徵涉及[[腎功能|腎功能]]異常、腎小管的鉀損失及鈉的過量吸收、與低鈉飲食及保鉀利尿藥(例如，[[阿米洛利|阿米洛利]](amiloride))的組合治療。李德爾氏綜合徵是非常罕見的，2008年在全球報告中只有不到30個家系或獨立病案被發現。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Rossier BC, Schild L |title=Epithelial sodium channel: mendelian versus essential hypertension |journal=Hypertension |volume=52 |issue=4 |pages=595–600 |date=October 2008 |pmid=18711011 |doi=10.1161/HYPERTENSIONAHA.107.097147 |url=http://hyper.ahajournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=18711011 |access-date=2014-12-06 |archive-date=2012-07-10 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120710225427/http://hyper.ahajournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=18711011 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==病因==
{{seealso|腎功能|腎生理學}}

這種綜合徵是由於在16p13-P12位點的遺傳變異所引起的上皮[[鈉離子通道|鈉離子通道]]([[上皮鈉離子通道|ENaC]](Epithelial sodium channel))失調。這些通道在某些細胞表面上被發現，在腎臟、肺及汗腺等被發現的這些細胞稱為"上皮細胞"(epithelial cell)。所述的{{lang|en|ENaC}}通道輸送鈉進入細胞。突變改變通道中的一個領域，以便它不再由[[泛素|泛素]][[蛋白酶体|蛋白酶体]]系統來正確地降解。<!--Specifically the PY motif in the protein is deleted or altered so the E3 ligase (Nedd4) no longer recognizes the channel. Therefore, there is increased activity of this channel leading to increased sodium reabsorption. The increased sodium reabsorption leads to hypertension due to an increase in extracellular volume.-->

